This paper proposes a new model-based reinforcement learning algorithm that infers unknown dynamics from known dynamics based on internal spectral properties of the environment. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), robotics (cs.RO), systems and control (cs.SY), and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
